# A version specific patch to fix the waddir is in the grimoire

with version stable 2.5.1.3
with base    MesaLib SDL_image SDL_mixer SDL_net doom_wad
with role    game
with trait   makej x11
with source  $SOURCEFORGE_URL prboom-plus/prboom-plus/${VERSION:0:7}/prboom-plus-$VERSION.tar.gz
with info    good 20120630
with info    last 20111204
with info    home http://prboom-plus.sourceforge.net
with info    cite 'port of the 3D FPS game called doom to POSIX
Possibily due to a bug you may have to run 
it from the present working directory of:
/usr/share/games/doom
so it can find prboom.wad'
